<subSubSection id="AAEA595FEB84725D935E3D84D57E61D8" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="CFC4185E75F0B710299D21D23C102A9B" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Diagnosis.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="51CA176AACA738B292824D8EE8C16C87" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
Characterized by pure white minute apothecia (&lt;0.3 mm in diameter) unlike 
<taxonomicName id="2D73D7BBBEAB7F21F813C72B1A55DAA4" class="Leotiomycetes" family="Lachnaceae" genus="L." kingdom="Fungi" lsidName="L. diminutum" order="Helotiales" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="species" species="diminutum">
<emphasis id="606844EA74AE6A54D9D25B47EABCB3E9" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">L. diminutum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
with rather colored apothecia, and smaller asci compared to similar species 
<taxonomicName id="A3B7980A1957FB0AC76273E773AD5F28" class="Ascomycetes" family="Discomycetes" genus="Lachnum" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Fungi" lsidName="Lachnum minutum" order="Helotiales" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="species" species="minutum">
<emphasis id="3EB14A8A962CB6526CE95D59F8F14F02" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Lachnum minutum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="099182F6F0AC5019A2E7598BEAD1ABD7" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
<emphasis id="2089FB19D994D63648CBA7C6B6E6B66A" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Holotype.</emphasis>
